<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Media Server - Getting Started</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: sans-serif; max-width: 800px;
           margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem; }
    h1 { color: #2B5797; }
    .service { background: #f5f5f5; padding: 1rem;
              margin: 1rem 0; border-radius: 8px; }
    .service h2 { margin-top: 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Welcome to ${DOMAIN} media server</h1>
  <p>Here's how to get set up with each service.</p>

  <div class="service">
    <h2>Movies & TV (Jellyfin)</h2>
    <p>URL: <a href="https://${DOMAIN}/jellyfin">https://${DOMAIN}/jellyfin</a></p>
    <p>Android: Install <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=org.jellyfin.mobile">Jellyfin</a> from the Play Store.</p>
    <p>Windows: Use any web browser, or install Jellyfin Media Player.</p>
  </div>


  <div class="service">
    <h2>Movies & TV (Plex)</h2>
    <p>URL: <a href="https://${DOMAIN}:${PLEX_HTTPS_PORT}/web">https://${DOMAIN}:${PLEX_HTTPS_PORT}/web</a></p>
    <p>Android / Windows / TV: Install <a href="https://www.plex.tv/media-server-downloads/#plex-app">Plex</a> and sign in, or use a web browser.</p>
    <p>Note: this entry only applies if the server admin has enabled Plex.</p>
  </div>


  <div class="service">
    <h2>Music (Navidrome)</h2>
    <p>URL: <a href="https://${DOMAIN}/music">https://${DOMAIN}/music</a></p>
    <p>Android: Install <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=app.symfonik.music.player">Symfonium</a> from the Play Store.</p>
    <p>Server URL in the app: https://${DOMAIN}/music</p>
  </div>


  <div class="service">
    <h2>Audiobooks & Podcasts (Audiobookshelf)</h2>
    <p>URL: <a href="https://${DOMAIN}/audiobookshelf">https://${DOMAIN}/audiobookshelf</a></p>
    <p>Android: Install <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.audiobookshelf.app">Audiobookshelf</a> from the Play Store.</p>
    <p>Server URL in the app: https://${DOMAIN}</p>
  </div>

  <h2>Need help or want to contribute?</h2>
  <p>Contact me and I'll get you sorted.</p>
</body>
</html>
